{"tid":618820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普傳向拉美招手 貿易合作選美棄中","createTime":"2018-04-06T06:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T12:28:10.000Z","uid":147314,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f0ea6fbc7ecae48552685a19a8b997955f90d3","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>特朗普傳向拉美招手 貿易合作選美棄中</strong><br />\n<br />\n有消息指，美國將再次加強拉攏盟友，在貿易議題上制衡中國。美方官員表示，美國總統特朗普下周出席秘魯舉行的美洲國家峰會時，將促請拉丁美洲國家不要與中國在貿易問題上合作。目前，美國已豁免對墨西哥、阿根廷和巴西進口鋼鋁徵稅。<br />\n<br />\n據路透引述美國高級官員表示，特朗普下周出席在秘魯舉行的美洲國家峰會時，將促拉美國家領導人在貿易問題上與美國、而非中國合作，並將再次強調中國貿易政策對拉美國家沒有成效，美國仍是拉美國家合作夥伴的首選。<br />\n<br />\n此前，美國前國務卿蒂勒森曾警告拉美勿與中國走近，批評中國擴大投資拉美為「經濟侵略」，警告拉美須考慮與中國走近的代價，並強調美國才是更好的生意夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n該官員估計，特朗普政府不會在峰會上就北美自由貿易協定（NAFTA）進行實質性討論。"},{"pid":"dcf78821e6e714849aad7a14ee4583f0fe8a23c3","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>歐日或聯手美國　向WTO投訴中國</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，據彭博報道，特朗普政府可能與歐盟和日本聯手，共同就中國歧視性的技術授權規定向WTO投訴。<br />\n<br />\n美國政治網站「Politico」早前引述歐盟委員會發言人表示，歐盟和美國在中國加大改革和市場開放方面，有完全一樣的擔憂。歐盟也將仔細調查向WTO投訴的可能性。Politico認為，針對中國竊取知識產權和強制技術轉讓等貿易行為，歐洲可能很快加入特朗普的貿易戰陣營。"},{"pid":"4b3275aadba2b484ccbccd789fccf3c3fde938ef","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2044926/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2044926%2F&d=UhcK7O4HZ2YeQOuwrYoL8m6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8cb230fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2044926/</a>"},{"pid":"de948af6cbf3842e7ddb79c6dec860f2e5a69c41","tid":618820,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c5d5eb6c3bb90a3d45c7714b98a5df4da9c481a","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>針對中國竊取知識產權和強制技術轉讓等貿易行為，<span style=\"color: red;\">歐洲可能很快加入特朗普的貿易戰陣營</span>。</blockquote><br />\n好心急，快少少得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7164ac31d372b5171601a60506fdccbcc4bf35","tid":618820,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"跟手強國又會打飛機<br />\n<br />\n向非洲國家招手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962b1c18c65ea74f8f5e7ef1fe1fea33cc6d1762","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed7164ac31d372b5171601a60506fdccbcc4bf35","tid":618820,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"跟手強國又會打飛機<br />\n<br />\n向非洲國家招手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"睇吓強國同五毛啲廢話講得幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72a197e235e65e078d2e61fbc491595d3336dbb","tid":618820,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"明知大陸實同巴西阿根廷買大豆<br />\n而家出定招先"},{"pid":"ab067abc2f5ab521be910c2915c3947e155b1cb8","tid":618820,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a72a197e235e65e078d2e61fbc491595d3336dbb","tid":618820,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"明知大陸實同巴西阿根廷買大豆<br />\n而家出定招先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"餓死支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc19f6d2700f8f200b20635b684ceec6c2a3924a","tid":618820,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"