ef5ad21a2f9e37f63","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"【歐盟、日本加入貿易戰】<br />\n【聯合美國商討中國知識產權問題】<br />\n<br />\n內地第一財經取得兩份世貿組織(WTO)文件，顯示歐盟和日本要求加入美國在WTO就中國歧視性的技術許可(跟國際知識產權協定相違背)，跟中國政府磋商。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟在WTO申請文件中指出，歐盟對外出口高科技產品和高科技知識密集型的服務產品，為此對歐盟產品的智慧財產權的保護具有重要性。歐盟方面估計每年對外出口的高科技產品在6800億歐元左右，其中歐盟每年向中國出口300億歐元的高科技產品。<br />\n<br />\n#歐日美聯盟<br />\n#知識產權<br />\n#貿易戰<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0b004148cbcd40dc597cc14e9f4b9024876b18","tid":618820,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"有排玩，好快唔再係1對1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82247e2415c4360d429d261a97018252e5ebc7d","tid":618820,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da0b004148cbcd40dc597cc14e9f4b9024876b18","tid":618820,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"有排玩，好快唔再係1對1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐預備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未洗出場住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365c1a18d6ca347ba3ea3032e2fdb7111418ace8","tid":618820,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吳京去咗邊，唔出嚟「雖遠必誅」嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"2e1ad73d63b572a4825c67ad4417300030fceb49","tid":618820,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"南美如果都唔侵支那玩, 咁就好睇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" cl